author: 傲娇大叔
txt_content:
本帖最后由 傲娇大叔 于 2020-3-14 15:45 编辑 

日志文件我已经放在附件里了。有各种类型的错误。（插件都是最新版，且下载时我都看好了适配1.12.2的，papi换了2.10.4和2.9.2的均不能解决）
比如
1.[ColorMOTD-Reremake] Unhandled exception occured in onPacketSending(PacketEvent) for ColorMOTD-Reremake
java.lang.NullPointerException: null
2.Error occurred while enabling Multiverse-Core v4.1.0-b775 (Is it up to date?)
3.Could not load 'plugins\[区域前置]worldguard-bukkit-7.0.2.jar' in folder 'plugins'
4.Could not load 'plugins\[按键]KeyboardMaster.jar' in folder 'plugins'
5.使用miaochat，已经安装了变量扩展，聊天界面依然一大堆占位符（我将聊天插件更换为Trchat后解决了）6.输入papi reload时报这个错Unexpected exception while parsing console command "papi reload"
7.[TrChat] Plugin TrChat v1.71 has failed to register events for class me.arasple.mc.trchat.chat.listeners.ListenerTabComplete because org/bukkit/event/player/PlayerCommandSendEvent does not exist.
等等......
麻烦过路大神帮忙解决
